OL,5, A teacher has been banned indefinitely 
OL,6, after a panel found he had sexual      
OL,7, relationships with two pupils.         
OL,9,FAndrew Batterham,57, was found to have 
OL,10,Fengaged in the relationships while a   
OL,11,Fteacher at the Leys School in Cambridge
OL,12,Fbetween 2000 and 2005.                 
OL,14,FHis actions "overstepped the boundary  
OL,15,Fby a wide, if not the widest, mark",   
OL,16,Fthe panel concluded.                   
OL,18,FA police investigation resulted in no  
OL,19,Ffurther action and Mr Batterham had    
OL,20,Fdenied the allegations.                
